title: Hella Vegan Eats
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Catering
description: Vegan food truck now with a permanent spot at Classic Cars West, a classic car showroom and local arts space, since Mar 2016. It's a restaurant and beer garden serving "festive food" like doughnuts, burgers, tacos, and burritos. Note that its food truck continues to operating in and around San Francisco Bay area - check its webpage for updates.
